357
00:29:17,250 --> 00:29:18,167
I'm fine.

358
00:29:20,125 --> 00:29:21,625
You just missed him.

359
00:29:24,625 --> 00:29:26,292
Shekhar was discharged.

360
00:29:27,083 --> 00:29:28,333
So, he had come to see you.

361
00:29:29,875 --> 00:29:31,083
