392
00:33:51,917 --> 00:33:53,833
Throw away that broken bicycle!

393
00:33:56,667 --> 00:33:58,917
Rama, it was just an accident.

394
00:34:02,417 --> 00:34:03,250
Here.

395
00:34:04,750 --> 00:34:05,625
Careful.

396
