00:36:34,167 --> 00:36:35,000
Ananya!

431
00:37:01,167 --> 00:37:02,500
-Dad--
-Dad, I don't want to get married.

432
00:37:03,792 --> 00:37:04,792
What?

433
00:37:06,625 --> 00:37:09,333
